 of travel demand coming from users. In other words, the services we\nenvisage in this work shift their operational mode to any intermediate point in\nthe range from a taxi-like door-to-door service to a bus-like service, with few\nserved stops and more passengers on-board.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Jul 2019 16:58:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Jul 2019 08:12:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-16"}
