 Experimental results demonstrate that the proposed pipeline\nsignificantly reduces the annotation effort and the resulting deep learning\nmethods outperform prior existing FA vessel detection methods by a significant\nmargin. A new public dataset, RECOVERY-FA19, is introduced that includes\nhigh-resolution ultra-widefield images and accurately labeled ground truth\nbinary vessel maps.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Jul 2019 17:27:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 10 May 2020 18:35:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-12"}
